{"tid":1521944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推］ 懷疑有人拎物資圖利","createTime":"2019-08-31T11:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:07:50.000Z","uid":247833,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"899d0b7d8d3ddf658e2ece138c2da8f44e44dbf7","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩發夢係灣仔行街<br />\n<br />\n朋友衰仔唔記得帶遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kn2aQ0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkn2aQ0c.jpg&h=2d85bd6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過呢間鋪頭諗住買把黑長遮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n把把遮都唔一樣色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買果時佢收走個保護套+極速開一開就比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後發現<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2cqr8Nc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2cqr8Nc.png&h=fb1311e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n把遮<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔似全新  兩邊都有燒過既洞</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無證據話佢地執物資去賣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但係為左唔好比人從中圖利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議大家係可轉賣既物資上貼d難清走既野<br />\n例如貼紙、噴漆咩都好</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461131315a25f20cf73d48b0cd013941073b1dd8","tid":1521944,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:41:36.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span>"},{"pid":"1335109adb393869ab8d4490f44b177bc1c652f7","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:41:52.000Z","msg":"自推5次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602261c3853e5cce8686106bc3e2022a34e7bc06","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"3a189b42db131101c1ba2bcef4bc4befe2f5221f","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:18.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9dbfe737884d192fd914a04eaaf39b39ebafa652","tid":1521944,"uid":314979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2O4wAvp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2O4wAvp.gif&h=728efc4d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73784b67e7541cd1714d7437b79976ca30146b95","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:31.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0b6ea0a893313962e56507897e873352b63aceb7","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8373cc7ae0f3504c55ed222f3f506d9c9c71aedc","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:42:53.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6df096b4bdbac82011ae07f5e40ae307b0f3f991","tid":1521944,"uid":84581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bd13c00007cdeeeb71665e70e84de6ce9c432a","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:46:23.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f8869f3c3620a793fd30f2e5913fae9811f5195e","tid":1521944,"uid":301633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"可以試試用家中煮食油試試。"},{"pid":"61835404d3eec707e04c5b348fec204f1d5d0e12","tid":1521944,"uid":247833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:07:50.000Z","msg":"推"}]}